  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Sorend is a water-based formula, which contains carob, melissa and sage. Elder inhabitants of
      Israel are known to use carob extract to ease sores in the mouth, due to the tannins which
      create a complex with various proteins and polysaccharides, thus creating an impenetrable
      layer covering the sores, allowing spontaneous healing.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
